WELCOME TO THIS HIGHLY LOVED 3 BED/3 FULL BATH (INCLUDING ENSUITE) SINGLE STORY HOME IN GUARD GATED GOLF COMMUNITY OF TUSCANY...w/NO BUILDER ASSESSMENT FEES. ENJOY HIGH 10FT CEILINGS, ARCHITECTURAL ACCENTS, FOUR 8FT GLASS SLIDERS &8FT PERIMETER DOORS. TILE THROUGHOUT ALL MAIN AREAS & ENSUITE. SPACIOUS KITCHEN OFFERS GRANITE COUNTERS, EXPANDED ISLAND W/2ND SINK &BREAKFAST BAR, BUILT IN DOUBLE OVENS & MICROWAVE. UNWIND IN THE OPEN FAMILY ROOM W/COZY 2 WAY FIREPLACE FOR WINTER... & CEILING FAN LIGHT FIXTURES FOR SPRING &SUMMER. 
MASTER BATH W/DUAL SINK VANITIES, RAIN-GLASS SHOWER/SEPARATE TUB COMBO AND WALK IN CLOSET W/CUSTOM BUILT-INS TO SUIT! 
RELAX OUTDOORS IN YOUR TRANQUIL BACKYARD W/PAVER PATIO, PLANTERS &TURF. THIS DREAM HOME OFFERS PRIME LOCATION IN A VIBRANT COMMUNITY FILLED W/AMENITIES TO ENRICH EVERY ASPECT OF LIFE...LOCATED JUST STEPS FROM CLUBHOUSE, NEWLY UPDATED FITNESS CENTER,COURTS, POOLS &PARK W/SCENIC WALKING TRAILS &ONSITE RESTAURANT. CALL &SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY!
